                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-11-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 7, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Conger reports the death of Earl Li at 11.15 on the morning of the 7th of
                    November.)</p>
